%% Deployment -- current local-only topology vs. recommended target topology
%% Referenced in: docs/deployment.md
graph TB
    subgraph Current["Current: confirmed local-only topology"]
        DevMachine[Single developer machine]
        DevMachine --> DF1[Dart Frog process]
        DevMachine --> OL1[Ollama process]
        DF1 <--> OL1
    end

    subgraph Target["Recommended target -- not yet implemented"]
        LB[Load Balancer]
        LB --> DF2a[Dart Frog replica A<br/>stateless container]
        LB --> DF2b[Dart Frog replica B<br/>stateless container]
        DF2a --> PG[(Postgres)]
        DF2b --> PG
        DF2a --> Inf[vLLM / managed inference API<br/>GPU-attached, scaled independently]
        DF2b --> Inf
    end

    style Current fill:#fff3cd,stroke:#664d03
    style Target fill:#d1e7dd,stroke:#0f5132
